overview: Two Moore's are better than one. Logan Moore and Josh Moore are mega-hot studs, desired by many, who all love to help them fulfill their needs. It's time for Logan and Josh to open up and give the guys who are 'Hungry for Moore' everything they've ever wanted and 'Moore'.
tagline: The studs are practically lining up for Logan as they satisfy their cravings of being 'Hungry for Moore'
title: Hungry for Moore
